{"tid":311610,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解米線唔係叫米粉，米粉唔係叫米線","createTime":"2017-07-06T18:11:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-06T23:57:27.000Z","uid":55514,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e719933b98d55363cb911df3f21130ddc6291c25","tid":311610,"uid":55514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T18:11:51.000Z","msg":"正常黎講，粉係比較粗，好似河粉咁，扁闊身，瀨粉比較粗。<br />\n但點解明明米粉明明咁幼，要叫米粉?<br />\n相反，米線係比較粗身，反而叫米&quot;線&quot;?線唔係應該好幼架咩?<br />\n我覺得應該米線叫米粉，米粉叫米線<br />\n咁先合理。<br />\nSorry for1999"},{"pid":"a131e42a48bb7db61675d7ff351ef9eca57ec0fe","tid":311610,"uid":103212,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T18:16:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb6219adc79e84c888de2d6d54911d5ed3afc330","tid":311610,"uid":103212,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T18:16:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b5b8b94112cdd34fc4b7cef33e68261e017eb017","tid":311610,"uid":30461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T18:17:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>衛福部規定，只有含米量超過50%以上的，才能稱為粉 <br />\n<br />\n唔夠就叫線 米線就係含米量唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n秒殺？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3626a0fe470aa42f6189a5a106d7d1ca40560624","tid":311610,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T18:22:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>衛福部規定，只有含米量超過50%以上的，才能稱為粉 <br />\n<br />\n唔夠就叫線 米線就係含米量唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n秒殺？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔講唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bf4eb18b486ee8a1475a4dc651f39b7abf9b4f1","tid":311610,"uid":425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-06T20:04:33.000Z","msg":"原來有人同我都係咁諗 疑惑左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor